OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a dry
OL,6,Fstart this evening rain will spread
OL,7,Feast across all parts for a time, Then
OL,8,Fdrier in the early hours before
OL,9,Ffurther rain reaches the Isles at the
OL,10,Fend of the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FRain will spread east in the
OL,13,Fmorning. Then drier for a time before
OL,14,Ffurther rain spread from the west in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon, mainly over the hills.
OL,16,FFreshening southerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
