OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of rain on Monday morning
OL,7,Fclearing to leave a dry afternoon.
OL,8,FBecoming dry and settled on Tuesday
OL,9,Fand Wednesday with overnight frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
